      <abstract>
        <p>The title compound, [1-(4-chlorophenyl)cyclopropyl](piperazin-1-yl)methanone, was synthesized and characterized by elemental analysis, IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, <sup>13</sup>C NMR and mass spectral data.</p>
      </abstract>
